    • isExternallyConditionalCacheHit

      @CanIgnoreReturnValue public ResponseVerifier<T> isExternallyConditionalCacheHit()
      Tests if this is a conditional cache hit resulting from a request that is conditionalized by the client and evaluated by the cache, rather than conditionalized by the cache and evaluated by the origin. The latter is checked with isConditionalCacheHit().
